# Deployment

## VPS (Backend)

- **IP**: `<VPS_IP>`
- **SSH**: `<SSH_USER>@<VPS_IP>` (password auth)
- **Code path**: `/opt/clawt/`
- **PM2 process**: `clawt-backend`
- **Port**: Backend runs on 4000, nginx proxies 80 → 4000

### Common Commands

VPS_PASSWORD is stored in the project root `.env` file (gitignored). Source it before running commands.

```bash
# Load password from .env
source .env

# SSH into VPS
sshpass -p "$VPS_PASSWORD" ssh -o StrictHostKeyChecking=no <SSH_USER>@<VPS_IP>

# Restart backend
sshpass -p "$VPS_PASSWORD" ssh -o StrictHostKeyChecking=no <SSH_USER>@<VPS_IP> 'pm2 restart clawt-backend'

# View logs
sshpass -p "$VPS_PASSWORD" ssh -o StrictHostKeyChecking=no <SSH_USER>@<VPS_IP> 'pm2 logs clawt-backend --lines 50'

# Sync code from local
sshpass -p "$VPS_PASSWORD" rsync -avz --exclude='node_modules' --exclude='.next' --exclude='data' \
  -e 'ssh -o StrictHostKeyChecking=no' \
  backend/ <SSH_USER>@<VPS_IP>:/opt/clawt/backend/
```

## Docker (Agent)

- **Image**: `clawt-agent:latest`
- **Base**: `node:20-slim` (linux/amd64)
- **Includes**: Python3, pip, git, curl (for skill execution)
- **Build**: `docker build -t clawt-agent:latest .` in `agent/` directory

## Vercel (Frontend)

- Deployed with SSO protection (team-level)
- Use Vercel MCP `get_access_to_vercel_url` tool to create shareable links
- Shareable URLs expire in 23 hours
- Project linked in `frontend/.vercel/project.json`

### Deploy Frontend

```bash
cd frontend && vercel --prod --yes
```

## Nginx Config

Located at `/etc/nginx/sites-available/skillsseal` on VPS (symlinked to sites-enabled).

```nginx
server {
    listen 80;
    server_name <VPS_IP>;

    location /api/ {
        proxy_pass http://127.0.0.1:4000;
        proxy_http_version 1.1;
        proxy_set_header Host $host;
        proxy_set_header X-Real-IP $remote_addr;
    }
}
```

## Backend .env Critical Variables

```
TOKEN_SECRET=<random-64-char-hex>
FRONTEND_URL=https://<vercel-url>
EIGENCOMPUTE_EMAIL=<ecloud-login>
EIGENCOMPUTE_PASSWORD=<ecloud-password>
DOCKER_IMAGE=clawt/agent:latest
PORT=4000
```
